text: Stade Lebon is a multi-use stadium in Angoulême, France. It is currently used mostly for football matches and is the home stadium of Angoulême CFC. The stadium is able to hold 6,500 people. ==External links== *World Stadiums entry Category:Angoulême-Soyaux Charente Lebon Category:Sports venues in Charente Category:Angoulême
